<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.1.6">
<l>pērāyi ramuṭaiya pērāḷaṉ pērāḷa ṉeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>ērārka ṉamakara kuṇṭalatta ṉeṇtōḷa ṉeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>nīrārma ḻaimukilē nīḷvaraiyē yokkumā leṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>kārārva yalamarum kaṇṇapurat tammāṉaik kaṇṭāḷ kollō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The one named with one-thousand names is the great lord,” she declares;</l>
<l>“He with beautiful, heavy makara earrings has eight arms,” she declares;</l>
<l>“He is indeed like rainclouds teeming with water and like a high mountain,” she declares.</l>
<l>Did she see the lord of Kaṇṇapuram where rain-filled paddy fields flourish?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
